Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 这里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关...关羽姐 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为答应了要把那本书借给小孔的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 你到底是怎么看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四话 视卒如婴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...关羽前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我是一年级的周仪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很尊敬前辈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐的礼物害得我都胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 老头子在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水镜老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给木造物驱虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要去买酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们总要做这种脏累活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水镜老师去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 从刚才开始就一直走神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋 马上就到成都学院了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一又和上次一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了不变成那样才要办和好会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刘备玄德大人真的是位很好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们带上便当 来开和好会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的家计...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的因为便当的费用就...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是社交舞的授业时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那个老师是我喜欢的肌肉型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作又增加了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像真的是个宝贝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢...丢死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 被你这么粗犷的手碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家害羞得做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着和你完全不配的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡闹什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为女子 不可以用那么粗暴的说话方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会坐在地上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得刚才的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事情是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是心露石做的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心露石是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上它的人会暴露本性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐怖的魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察觉出佩戴者内心深处的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配佩戴者的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在摸什么啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI BABY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摆出这么可怕的脸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他带上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和你来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是黄忠的本性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是个花和尚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦耶 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始两个人来享受一下我的技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头还是那么厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想被打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 关羽姐 胸部颤颤的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然关羽姐与本大爷更合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI BABY 今天我要好好摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我去死吧 花和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无南无
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这是最后的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好给你的书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德  果然你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始关羽姐就一直走神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有发烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走...要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去后山大树下看书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子 喜欢看书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张飞也是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事 你找打哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请不要打我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救我 小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我还...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道玄德的真正心意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是怎么看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你今天很奇怪呢 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不去吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上它的人会暴露本性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察觉出佩戴者内心深处的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配佩戴者的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心露石项链不能就这么放着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被谁得到有可能会再次引起麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 黄忠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吃饭的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守好那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我来看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里睡着 会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔 身上有着婴儿般的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道 好想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道 想知道 想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让你请我吃什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我请客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸了别人你好意思不赔罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是南阳的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小孔醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德的胸部好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的梦话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关羽姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为闻到了关羽姐的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的味道 味道 味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...想送你做礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这样看着 我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个项链闪闪的 真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 快带上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 心情有没有惴惴不安...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 很想沉浸在书里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说想对我说些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有点闷热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是不喜欢的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚...刚刚你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 关羽姐 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也喜欢小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有张飞和子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐也带上看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来捣乱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么站在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用看护了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是刚才的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么关羽姐戴着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 关羽姐 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听见了当家的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐把玄德给带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是心露石项链的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是赵云子龙的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我换衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在桃园立誓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会变成这样的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是关羽姐 今天不是练武的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你们两个人都要陪我练武吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很高兴 不过好为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那个项链有那么不可思议的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个要是真正打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不能全身而退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定是哪一方会丢掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么不吉利的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切磋虽然是可以的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对我们的当家无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德是不会交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想拆散我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就等着丧命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了让你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去阻止看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么两个一定要争斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 事情变得这么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对当家做出了这么不敬的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不允许自己剥夺自己性命的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙子曰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视卒如婴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对待士兵要像对待婴儿般爱护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于当家来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们就像是婴儿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当家的总是要深思熟虑考虑一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐要是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道谁会最难过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我作为当家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要知道你和子龙两个人争斗的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上这个项链
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会无意识地陷入打斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策伯符 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力很非常强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我带上的时候什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 小刘 今天是和好日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好日的话 我应该告诉你的是下周啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这种事情当然是越早越好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天都为我浪费掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管今天有没有成果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直失忆下去并不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果恢复了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙又会变成以前的吕布奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭再回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把她交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的突然到访 没有给您添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋来了以后 每天都好开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋才是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们在一起 有没有觉得好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者好累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道仲谋的真心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 用这个项链的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策小姐 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙权小姐？孙权小姐她...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仲谋原来是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五话 非危不战
